{"1":{"w":[{"b":"0.15","h":"1.15","c":"قُلْ","d":"qul","e":"katakanlah"},{"b":"0.44","h":"1.68","c":"يَاأَيُّهَا","d":"yāayyuhā","e":"wahai"},{"b":"3.3","h":"4.93","c":"الْكَافِرُونَ","d":"l-kāfirūna","e":"orang-orang kafir"}],"a":{"g":"Say, \"O disbelievers,","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                ينبغي إذا هم بالخروج أن يصلي ركعتين أولا يقرأ في الأولى بعد الفاتحة قل يا أيها الكافرون وفي الثانية الإخلاص\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, when one intends to depart, he should first pray two units [rak'atayn]. In the first, after the Opening [al-Fatiha], he should recite: \"Say, 'O you disbelievers [al-Kafirun]'\" and in the second, \"Sincerity [al-Ikhlas].\"\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"2":{"w":[{"b":"0.1","h":"0.4","c":"لَا","d":"lā","e":"tidak"},{"b":"1.7","h":"2.14","c":"أَعْبُدُ","d":"aʿbudu","e":"aku menyembah"},{"b":"3.4","h":"3.6","c":"مَا","d":"mā","e":"apa"},{"b":"3.7","h":"4.33","c":"تَعْبُدُونَ","d":"taʿbudūna","e":"kamu sembah"}],"a":{"g":"I do not worship what you worship."}},"3":{"w":[{"b":"0.07","h":"0.65","c":"وَلَا","d":"walā","e":"dan tidak"},{"b":"2.0","h":"2.39","c":"أَنْتُمْ","d":"antum","e":"kamu"},{"b":"3.7","h":"4.14","c":"عَابِدُونَ","d":"ʿābidūna","e":"menyembah"},{"b":"5.1","h":"6.61","c":"مَا","d":"mā","e":"apa"},{"b":"6.9","h":"8.28","c":"أَعْبُدُ","d":"aʿbudu","e":"aku sembah"}],"a":{"g":"Nor are you worshippers of what I worship."}},"4":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","h":"0.4","c":"وَلَا","d":"walā","e":"dan bukanlah"},{"b":"2.0","h":"2.24","c":"أَنَا","d":"anā",